com.siperian.sif.message.event.am

Class AmEventBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.event.am.AmEventBase

  • public abstract class AmEventBase
extends Object
    Base class extended by ORS package specific AmEvent objects that are created by JmsEventSchemaGenerator. Only amRuleUid is represented in castor and extended by AmEvent objects; other members are used to facilitate AM rules engine in populating an AmRuleEvent message with data.
    Author:
    echoi
